          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "祸来难救，负荆早向辕门叩。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（高杰恼。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "俺高杰，乃元帅标下先锋。元帅不加护庇，倒叫与三镇服礼，可不羞死人也。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "罢，罢，罢！看来元帅也不能用俺了。不免领兵渡江，另做事业去吧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（香柳娘） 这屈辱怎当，这屈辱怎当，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "渡过大江头，事业从新做。"
        },
        {
          "character": "高杰",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "三军快来，随俺前去。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（众兵卒同上，呐喊摇旗同下。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘泽清",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "啊呀呀！高杰竟要过江了。想江南有他的党羽，不日要领来与俺厮闹。俺也早"
        },
        {
          "character": "刘泽清",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "去约会黄、刘二镇，多带人马，到此迎敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（香柳娘） 笑力穷远走，笑力穷远走，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "长江洗羞，防他重来作寇。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（刘泽清下。侯方域呆。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "不料局势如此，教俺怎生收救。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（香柳娘） 恨山河半倾，恨山河半倾，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "怎能重构；人心瓦解忘恩旧。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（侯方域向南望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那高杰竟是反了。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（香柳娘） 看扬扬渡江，看扬扬渡江，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "旗帜乱中流，直入南徐口。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（侯方域向北望。）"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "那刘泽清也急忙北去，要约会三镇人马，全来迎敌。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（香柳娘） 这烟尘偏有，这烟尘偏有，"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "好叫俺元帅搔头，参谋搓手。"
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "白",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "且回复了阁部，再作计较。正是："
        },
        {
          "character": "侯方域",
          "line_type": "念",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "堂堂开府辖通侯，江北淮南数上游。只恐楼船与铁马，一时都羡好扬州。"
        },
        {
          "character": null,
          "line_type": "stage_direction",
          "musical_style": null,
          "style_family": null,
          "text": "（侯方域下。）"
        }
      ],
